	<string name="about_title">About MDriod</string>
	<string name="about_content">
		This is a BETA test version.\n
		MDroid Music Quiz is a game which loads music from local SDCard or Phone Memory and turns them into exciting music quiz game.\n	
	</string>

	<string name="agreement">
		Congratulations and thank you for installing MDroid.
		\n\nBefore you start here are some quick introductions.
		\n\nTime Mode: In time mode one song will be played and four choices is given, 
		your goal is to choose the correct match of the song as fast as possible. 
		\n*Every wrong guess will add a extra 5 seconds.
		\n\nGeneral Hints: We suggest you have a least 20 song on your device.
		Insufficient songs will reduce interest of the game.
		\n\nYou can also
		check allow repeat in settings page if you do not have enough songs to
		play with.
		\n\nMost importantly, HAVE FUN, lot of it!
	</string>

